item.title: CVE-2024-10119|2024-10-18T04:09:15.991Z -- secom -- wrtm326
item.description: The wireless router WRTM326 from SECOM does not properly validate a specific parameter. An unauthenticated remote attacker could execute arbitrary system commands by sending crafted requests.
